data.description: BBeautiful 4-bedroom energy efficient home in a prime location!  This home includes solar panels and is backed by a 13kwh Tesla power-wall, which provides up to 12 hours of power if the lights go out.  In addition, enjoy the low electric bills! There is also a carbon-based water filtration system that provides filtered water throughout the home.  The reverse osmosis filter near the kitchen sink provides you with the cleanest and purest drinking water.  Vivint Security provides your home with top notch safety, with the doorbell camera visible from the smart panel and smart phone. Garage door opens with remote or smart phone. Prime location- Minutes from Cimarron Hills Golf and Country Club, HEB Center, Lakeline Mall, Whole Foods, Kalahari Resorts and Indoor Waterpark, and more!  Take advantage of the walking trails, dog park, and playground just steps from your home!
